com.bigdata.rdf.graph

Interface IGASSchedulerImpl

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IGASScheduler
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CHMScheduler, STScheduler, TLScheduler, TLScheduler2

    public interface IGASSchedulerImpl
extends IGASScheduler
    Extended IGASScheduler interface. This interface is exposed to the implementation of the GAS Engine. The methods on this interface are NOT for use by the IGASProgram and MIGHT NOT (really, should not) be available on the IGASScheduler supplied to an IGASProgram.
    Author:
    Bryan Thompson
